      "content": "But isn't that just a coping mechanism? Like, we just invent these little stories—purpose, connection, legacy—to distract ourselves from the fact that we're just biochemical accidents in a dying system. It feels dishonest to call it \"freedom\" when it's really just a desperate attempt to ignore the scale of the void. If the end result is always zero, then the math says the struggle is just wasted energy.",
